org.odpi.openmetadata.repositoryservices.enterprise.repositoryconnector.accumulators.RelationshipHistoryAccumulator
public class RelationshipHistoryAccumulator extends RelationshipsAccumulator
RelationshipHistoryAccumulator accumulates and validates historical versions of relationships received from a collection of open metadata repositories. It removes duplicates from the list but preserves one instance of each version. This class may be called simultaneously from different threads, so it must be thread-safe.
